  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction à MLT</title>

    <para><application>MLT</application> package is the Media Lovin Toolkit.
    It is an open source multimedia framework, designed et developed for
    television broadcasting. It provides a toolkit for broadcasters, video
    editors, media players, transcoders, web streamers et many more types of
    applications.</para>

    &lfs77_checked; &gcc5_checked;

